ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectOrder to Remit Part I License Fees Paid or Payable by all Broadcasting Licensees
PrecisOrder remitting the Part I Licence fees paid or payable by all licensees under paragraph 3(a) of the BROADCASTING LICENCE FEE REGULATIONS, 1997, in respect of the fiscal year 2020-2021 so that they are better positioned to deal with the COVID-19 emergency.
